<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35D8606FFFE40F959" box="[402,436,1670,1691]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">a–c</emphasis>
): 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35DD206FFFE26F959" box="[454,466,1670,1691]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">a</emphasis>
— dorsal view of female, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35ED206FCFD26F958" box="[710,722,1669,1690]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">b</emphasis>
— frontal view of head of female, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF3580C06FFFBD5F959" box="[1048,1057,1670,1691]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">c</emphasis>
— male genitalia; 
<taxonomicName id="4AA6D0DA320BFFF35CBE06D9FEFBF977" box="[170,271,1696,1717]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Cheilosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="406" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aruralis">
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35CBE06D9FEFBF977" box="[170,271,1696,1717]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">C. aruralis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, female (
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35D7E06D9FE7CF977" box="[362,392,1696,1717]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">d–f</emphasis>
): 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35D8806D9FE5CF977" box="[412,424,1696,1717]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">d</emphasis>
— dorsal view, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35E5006D9FDBAF977" box="[580,590,1696,1717]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">e</emphasis>
— frontal view of head, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35F2A06D9FCB1F977" box="[830,837,1696,1717]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">f</emphasis>
— lateral view; 
<taxonomicName id="4AA6D0DA320BFFF35FF406D9FB6CF977" baseAuthorityName="Fallen" baseAuthorityYear="1817" box="[992,1176,1696,1717]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Cheilosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="406" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scutellata">
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35FF406D9FB6CF977" box="[992,1176,1696,1717]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">Cheilosia scutellata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
male (
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35CA606C2FF3BF912" box="[178,207,1723,1744]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">g–i</emphasis>
): 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35CF606C2FF18F912" box="[226,236,1723,1744]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">g</emphasis>
— lateral view, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35D9206C3FE66F90D" box="[390,402,1722,1743]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">h</emphasis>
— frontal view of head, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35E6906C2FD70F912" box="[637,644,1723,1744]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">i</emphasis>
— genitalia.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<subSubSection id="C5BCF8D2320BFFF05CBE069CFD5DFE48" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="407" pageId="5" pageNumber="406" type="description">
<paragraph id="8D19AB59320BFFF35CBE069CFB54F8F2" blockId="5.[170,1229,1765,1840]" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">
Рис. 3. 
<taxonomicName id="4AA6D0DA320BFFF35CE5069CFE7BF938" baseAuthorityName="Preyssler" baseAuthorityYear="1798" box="[241,399,1765,1786]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Cheilosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="406" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rufipes">
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35CE5069CFE7BF938" box="[241,399,1765,1786]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">Cheilosia rufipes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35D88069FFE4AF939" box="[412,446,1766,1787]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">a–c</emphasis>
): 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35DC5069FFE29F939" box="[465,477,1766,1787]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">a</emphasis>
— самка, вид снизу, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35EA0069CFD34F938" box="[692,704,1765,1786]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">b</emphasis>
— голова самки, фронтальный вид, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35823069FFBB4F939" box="[1079,1088,1766,1787]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">c</emphasis>
— гениталии самца; 
<taxonomicName id="4AA6D0DA320BFFF35CE00779FEA8F8D7" box="[244,348,1792,1813]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Cheilosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="406" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aruralis">
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35CE00779FEA8F8D7" box="[244,348,1792,1813]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">C. aruralis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, самка (
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35DA10779FE20F8D7" box="[437,468,1792,1813]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">d–f</emphasis>
): 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35DFE0779FE02F8D7" box="[490,502,1792,1813]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">d</emphasis>
— вид сверху, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35E880779FD52F8D7" box="[668,678,1792,1813]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">e</emphasis>
— голова, фронтальный вид, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35FF30779FC1AF8D7" box="[999,1006,1792,1813]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">f</emphasis>
— латеральный вид; 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35CBE0763FE93F8ED" box="[170,359,1818,1839]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">
<taxonomicName id="4AA6D0DA320BFFF35CBE0763FE97F8ED" baseAuthorityName="Fallen" baseAuthorityYear="1817" box="[170,355,1818,1839]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Cheilosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="406" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scutellata">Cheilosia scutellata</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
самец (
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35DA10762FE26F8F2" box="[437,466,1819,1840]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">g–i</emphasis>
): 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35DF10762FE1BF8F2" box="[485,495,1819,1840]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">g</emphasis>
— латеральный вид, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF35EDE0763FD22F8ED" box="[714,726,1818,1839]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">h</emphasis>
— голова, фронтальный вид, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320BFFF3581C0762FBFBF8F2" box="[1032,1039,1819,1840]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">i</emphasis>
— гениталии.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8D19AB593208FFF05CCF00C9FD45FEC8" blockId="6.[166,1225,175,394]" pageId="6" pageNumber="407">
D i s t r i b u t i o n. From Fennoscandia southwards to Northern Africa; from Britain (southern 
<collectingCountry id="F5B1EBC93208FFF05D3600B6FE72FF28" box="[290,390,207,234]" name="United Kingdom" pageId="6" pageNumber="407">England</collectingCountry>
) eastwards through most of Europe into Siberia and on to the Pacific coast, including 
<collectingCountry id="F5B1EBC93208FFF05D730089FE58FEC8" box="[359,428,240,266]" name="Japan" pageId="6" pageNumber="407">Japan</collectingCountry>
; 
<collectingCountry id="F5B1EBC93208FFF05DA30089FE1DFEC8" box="[439,489,240,266]" name="Iran" pageId="6" pageNumber="407">Iran</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="E937D6A83208FFF05DE30096FD51FEC8" author="Gilasian, E." box="[503,677,239,266]" pageId="6" pageNumber="407" pagination="75 - 76" refId="ref6509" refString="Gilasian, E. New record of one genus and six species of Syrphidae (Diptera) from Iran // J. Entomological Society of Iran. - 2005. - 25, N 1. - P. 75 - 76." type="book chapter" year="2005">Gilasian, 2005</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8D19AB593208FFF05CCF0169FD5DFE48" blockId="6.[166,1225,175,394]" pageId="6" pageNumber="407">
D i a g n o s t i c c h a r a c t e r s. Eye bare; facial knob bare and broad from above semicircular running from eye margin to eye margin; 3rd segment of antenna bright red (
<figureCitation id="159DB7DC3208FFF058930156FB37FE8B" box="[1159,1219,303,329]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="5.[170,203,1669,1691]" captionTargetBox="[173,1228,862,1644]" captionTargetId="figure-318@5.[169,1228,862,1644]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="Fig. 3. Cheilosia rufipes (a–c): a — dorsal view of female, b — frontal view of head of female, c — male genitalia; C. aruralis, female (d–f): d — dorsal view, e — frontal view of head, f — lateral view; Cheilosia scutellata male (g–i): g — lateral view, h — frontal view of head, i — genitalia." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6449155" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6449155/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="407">fig. 3</figureCitation>
, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B3208FFF05CB20136FF40FEAB" box="[166,180,335,361]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="407">b</emphasis>
), anterior anepisternum with hairs along posterodorsal rim; thoracic dorsum with coarse punctuation (
<figureCitation id="159DB7DC3208FFF05D520116FE75FE4B" box="[326,385,367,393]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="5.[170,203,1669,1691]" captionTargetBox="[173,1228,862,1644]" captionTargetId="figure-318@5.[169,1228,862,1644]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="Fig. 3. Cheilosia rufipes (a–c): a — dorsal view of female, b — frontal view of head of female, c — male genitalia; C. aruralis, female (d–f): d — dorsal view, e — frontal view of head, f — lateral view; Cheilosia scutellata male (g–i): g — lateral view, h — frontal view of head, i — genitalia." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6449155" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6449155/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="407">fig. 3</figureCitation>
, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B3208FFF05D9A0109FE68FE4B" box="[398,412,368,393]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="407">a</emphasis>
); genitalia as (
<figureCitation id="159DB7DC3208FFF05E510116FD75FE4B" box="[581,641,367,393]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="5.[170,203,1669,1691]" captionTargetBox="[173,1228,862,1644]" captionTargetId="figure-318@5.[169,1228,862,1644]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="Fig. 3. Cheilosia rufipes (a–c): a — dorsal view of female, b — frontal view of head of female, c — male genitalia; C. aruralis, female (d–f): d — dorsal view, e — frontal view of head, f — lateral view; Cheilosia scutellata male (g–i): g — lateral view, h — frontal view of head, i — genitalia." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6449155" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6449155/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="407">fig. 3</figureCitation>
, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B3208FFF05E990109FD6CFE4B" box="[653,664,368,393]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="407">c</emphasis>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
